{
  "stem": "26609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was not anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She liked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then she said, would you like your mother to come to see us?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, who speaks, at home, such a good Polish?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother spoke a very good Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said, you're exceptional, because Jews don't speak well Polish-- not 'gramatyczny.' Was that true of that period?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was that true of that time?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I remember that my mother used to say that she was ashamed some mothers-- some Jewish people-- did not attend school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't know how to write Polish or read Polish, and she was ashamed of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, everybody, when you live in a country, as we do, you should learn the language of the country.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother was a very intelligent [BACKGROUND NOISE] and educated person, as I said later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the Poles were-- as I said before, the Ukraines were very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, they too, they-- they didn't like the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Poles didn't like the Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Jews didn't like the Poles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were not many good neighbors, as we have here-- Polish ones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But some were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like, we lived, as I mentioned before, on a part of Grodek where there were just scattered a few Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We lived near a Ukrainian church.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother used-- around the corner, somehow she met the priest of the church.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In Polish we say [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She met him around the corner, somehow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he liked very much my mother, because he said there are not many people with whom he can talk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He talked with my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She loved to talk about religions-- not only Jewish, other religions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they formed just a friendship.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
